arge mines.<br></li><li>Get the key to all the chests and beat the time records to escape. Will you get more points than your friends?<br></li><li>Now the flea dives!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768990/extras/cffec2a0177b8cc893c7fabef9c0953f.poster.avif?t=1732184344\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768990/extras/cffec2a0177b8cc893c7fabef9c0953f.webm?t=1732184344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768990/extras/cffec2a0177b8cc893c7fabef9c0953f.mp4?t=1732184344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Today you can relive one of these nostalgic games in an enhanced version. All that is good about vintage video games, with the best of today's action games.<br><br>Download it now and enjoy this addictive game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768990/extras/c65efde418c5ddf24110772d217d696a.avif?t=1732184344\" width=610 height=300 /></span>",
